posts.post_content:
"Are you interested?"

Yes-- I purchase collections ranging from poor condition, bulk commons, mid-grade partial sets, to ultra-hi grade raw and registry sets and everything autographed, memorabilia, or cardboard in between.

I offer hassle free, lightning speed transactions at any dollar value via paypal, check, and bank wire.

There is no collection too large or small and I am able to travel for 6 and 7 figure transactions.

Please feel free to message me on the forums or email me at the address in my signature below.

I look forward to working with you on all of your collectible asset liquidity needs.

Kind Regards,

Sean
